                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I swear these are my shoes—I had a threepenny-piece and a farthing in my pocket—my chest was open—some one must have come down while I was asleep.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I bought the shoes in Petticoat-lane, about two months ago.</p>
